pageContext.claim: “You know who was smoked today? President Barack Hussein Obama. He had 12 people in seven cars. Did you hear, though? No, he draws, he draws flies. I've never seen -- He draws -- He had no, he had no people. I thought he'd have some people, and he brought Bon Jovi along. You know what happened to Bon Jovi? They increased the crowd by 22 people. Can you believe it? And then Joe spoke and that crowd left.”
pageContext.analysis: Reports say hundreds of cars which, at five people per car, could contain thousands of people attended these Obama events.
